snippet.title: Palia – Launch Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Palia is available now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/palia-switch/ 

Live the cozy adventure of your dreams in a breathtaking new world. Unravel a deep mystery about what happened to ancient humans as you reappear in a world alongside other players! Explore a vibrant land full of wonder and charm as you build a life and home for yourself with Palia, a free-to-play cozy MMO game!  

#Palia #NintendoSwitch 

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! https://www.nintendo.com/us/
